Listing of media in KOMODO

Here, we list all media in the KOMODO database. Media identification numbers are inherited from the DSMZ listings. These media numbers are altered in cases where special instructions were available for growing specific strains or when alternative components were listed within a medium, either within the media descriptions themselves, or elsewhere in the DSMZ resources. When this was the case, we modified the media numbers by adding a delimiter (either a period '.' or an underscore '_') and then some number or modifier. Therefore, the number that comes before the delimiter is the exact medium number that is listed in DSMZ, and the code after the delimiter denotes some modification on that base medium. Click any of the media for a list of components in it, along with their molar concentrations (or gram per liter concentrations, in the case of undefined components).
